parameters.name: LogsDownloadAttributes
parameters.description:
The access log forwarding rule. Parameters:

*   **LogProject**: the name of the project of Log Service.
*   **LogStore**: the name of the Logstore of Log Service.
*   **LoadBalancerId**: the ID of the CLB instance.

parameters.name: RegionId
parameters.description: The region ID of the CLB instance.

parameters.name: Tags
parameters.description: The tags that are added to the CLB instance. The tags must be key-value pairs that are contained in a JSON dictionary.
